  "description": "<h3>Steam Store Description (from <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/game/micro-mages/adblurbs\">Ad Blurbs</a>)</h3>Micro Mages is a platform game developed for the original 8-bit NES console. Now on Steam!<br><br>Slip into your wizard robes and enter the Demon Fortress, home of great treasure and ghastly creatures alike. Shoot and wall-jump your way up the fortress's towers and battle the evil bosses lurking at the top.<br><br>Play solo or join forces with your friends. This game supports up to 4 players. Will you help each other overcome the dangerous traps built to stop nosy adventurers or will you turn on your comrades to snatch the high score? No downtime: If you die while at least one other player is still alive, you will turn into a ghost and can help by freezing enemies. Try to open crates and treasure chests to find a Fairy or Feather that will bring you back to life.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>1 to 4 players simultaneous<br></li><li>Cooperate or compete for score<br></li><li>26 spooky levels (normal + hard modes)<br></li><li>Dangerous traps, monsters and bosses<br></li><li>Ancient secrets<br></li><li>Password function allows you to continue your game - in classic NES fashion<br></li><li>ROM included in installation folder (right-click the game in your Steam library, click Properties/Local Files/Browse Local Files...)<br></li><li><i>You can access a colorful manual in the style of classic NES instruction booklets without buying the game, check the links on the right side of this store page!</i></li></ul>",
